 reservation and then when he found out the water quality, he cancelled.\\\"\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"\\\"He made a reservation and then when he found out the water quality, he cancelled.\\\"\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}},{\"type\":\"subheadline\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Leaky cesspits\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Leaky cesspits\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}}]}}],\"level\":2}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"model\":{\"suitableForAbridgement\":false,\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Southern Water said it was working hard to find the source of the contaminants and to make bathing water safe. \",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Southern Water said it was working hard to find the source of the contaminants and to make bathing water safe. \",\"attributes\":[]}}]}},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Nick Mills, director of environment innovation, said it was working on connecting some leaky private cesspits to its sewers as well as other sources.\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"Nick Mills, director of environment innovation, said it was working on connecting some leaky private cesspits to its sewers as well as other sources.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"He said: \\\"In St Mary\'s Bay, we take extra samples with the Environment Agency to speciate what the source is.\",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"He said: \\\"In St Mary\'s Bay, we take extra samples with the Environment Agency to speciate what the source is.\",\"attributes\":[]}}]}},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"\\\"And in that case we found a really strong correlation with seabird markers. \",\"blocks\":[{\"type\":\"fragment\",\"model\":{\"text\":\"\\\"And in that case we found a really strong correlation with seabird mar