e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/5e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/5e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/5e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/5e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/5e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/5e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 1536w\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/5e84/live/fa17d2f0-5327-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"Biffa / Mitchells &amp; Butlers Fourteen men and women volunteers in orange hi viz jackets at a beach on a sunny day. They are smiling at the camera. Everyone is holding a collection bag and some are holding litter pickers. The sea could be seen behind them.\" class=\"sc-a34861b-0 efFcac\"><span class=\"sc-a34861b-2 hesJxn\">Biffa / Mitchells &amp; Butlers</span></div></div><div data-component=\"caption-block\" class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 bdPeAJ\"><figcaption class=\"sc-8353772e-0 iUqqeb\">Volunteers from Biffa and Mitchells &amp; Butlers collected 60kg of waste at Southbourne beach on 17 July<!-- --></figcaption></div></figure><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 dlWCEZ\"><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">More than 60kg (9.5st) of waste has been removed from a beach during a big litter pick.<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">Volunteers from waste management company Biffa and restaurant company Mitchells &amp; Butlers joined forces to do a clean off at Southbourne beach in Bournemouth, Dorset on 17 July.<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">The results have now come out to show the quantity of collected litter, which included bottles, cans, discarded clothes, and hazardous marine waste such as fishing wire.<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">A Biffa spokesperson said the event had contributed to the worldwide initiative <!-- --><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.plasticfreejuly.org/\" class=\"sc-c9299ecf-0 beIoQm\">Plastic Free July<!-- --></a>.<!-- --></p></div><div data-testid=\"ad-unit\" data-component=\"ad-slot\" class=\"sc-ad65179a-0 irVkns\"><div data-testid=\"dotcom-mid_1\" id=\"dotcom-mid_1\" class=\"dotcom-ad\"></div></div><figure><div data-component=\"image-block\" class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 jFCfG\"><div data-testid=\"image\" class=\"sc-a34861b-1 jxzoZC\"><img src=\"https://www.bbc.com/bbcx/grey-placeholder.png\" class=\"sc-a34861b-0 cOpVbP hide-when-no-script\"><img sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 1008px) 66vw, 96vw\" srcset=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 240w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 320w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 480w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 640w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 800w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 1024w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1536/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp 1536w\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/f1e2/live/05046280-532a-11ef-ab56-498a6bc5f07d.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Biffa / Mitchells &amp; Butlers Volunteer in an orange hi viz Biffa jacket collects litter at a beach on an overcast day. He\'s facing away from the camera. Other volunteers can be seen ahead in the distance.\" class=\"sc-a34861b-0 efFcac\"><span class=\"sc-a34861b-2 hesJxn\">Biffa / Mitchells &amp; Butlers</span></div></div><div data-component=\"caption-block\" class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 bdPeAJ\"><figcaption class=\"sc-8353772e-0 iUqqeb\">Results show dozens of bottles and cans, and even fishing wire have been picket up during the event<!-- --></figcaption></div></figure><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 dlWCEZ\"><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">It was organised by workers from Biffa&rsquo;s Poole depot and members of Mitchells &amp; Butlers kitchen development team.<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">Biffa said that that recyclable waste, including plastic and glass bottles, had been put back into the circular economy to be transformed into new products.<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">Non-recyclable general waste had been sent to an energy-from-waste facility to be converted into electricity.<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">Biffa&rsquo;s head of corporate accounts Mark Chapman, who took part in the litter pick, said they took \"great pride\" in supporting local sustainability projects.<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">\"We were thrilled to work alongside our customer Mitchells &amp; Butlers for the litter pick at Southbourne beach, helping to ensure our beautiful coastline is protected for everyone&rsquo;s enjoyment.&rdquo;<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">David Gallacher, Mitchells &amp; Butlers divisional director, said their partnership \"represents a ground-breaking approach to waste management\".<!-- --></p><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fezwLZ\">Biffa said that it had helped the company divert \"10,500 tonnes of food waste from landfill to energy recovery\" since October 2023.<!-- --></p></div><div data-testid=\"ad-unit\" data-component=\"ad-slot\" class=\"sc-ad65179a-0 irVkns\"><div data-testid=\"dotcom-mid_2\" id=\"dotcom-mid_2\" class=\"dotcom-ad\"></div></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 dlWCEZ\"><p class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-